headline: Corpay Cross-Border Using Blockchain Technology to Facilitate Client FX Conversions
summary: TORONTO, August 05, 2025--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business can facilitate client foreign exchange (FX) conversions using J.P. Morgan’s Kinexys Digital Payments blockchain.
